  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZTg0NjE2OWJmZTc3ZTA1Y2E4MDZiLmpwZz93aWR0aD00OTYmaGVpZ2h0PTY2Nw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e846169bfe77e05ca806b.jpg?width=496&amp;height=667\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e846169bfe77e05ca806b.jpg?width=496&amp;height=667\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/e846169bfe77e05ca806b.jpg?width=496&amp;height=667\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOWVkMDU4MDQ0ZDk0NjljZWU1MTdjLmpwZz93aWR0aD01MDkmaGVpZ2h0PTg0Mg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9ed058044d9469cee517c.jpg?width=509&amp;height=842\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9ed058044d9469cee517c.jpg?width=509&amp;height=842\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9ed058044d9469cee517c.jpg?width=509&amp;height=842\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGMzNzk4ZThhMzE0YzAzMmIwNGQ3LmpwZz93aWR0aD01MDkmaGVpZ2h0PTc3MQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c3798e8a314c032b04d7.jpg?width=509&amp;height=771\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c3798e8a314c032b04d7.jpg?width=509&amp;height=771\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4c3798e8a314c032b04d7.jpg?width=509&amp;height=771\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n看完后会不会觉得<mark>支那人</mark>可怜又可恶？<br/>\n可是但凡有点社会常识的就知道想要从<mark>支那</mark>医院里不退病房先退押金钱是不可能的事情，可见这个故事就是段子手编的。<br/>\n但这个段子手是不是<mark>支那人</mark>？故事里<mark>支那人</mark>的坏是假的话，那编故事的<mark>支那人</mark>的坏就是真的。二者必局其一，最终结论还是<mark>支那人</mark>是坏逼。\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
